name: Java Tree
body:
Download the latest jar artifacts here:
https://sourceforge.net/projects/javatree/files/javatree/1.0/

Original project home: https://sourceforge.net/projects/javatree/
tagline: This project aims to provide an extensible Tree interface to supplement the Java Collections framework, making full use of Java 5 generics. At least one reference implementation will be provided as part of the scope of this project.
